# Kichewa Trading Agencies Website

This is a fully responsive, front-end website project for **Kichewa Trading Agencies**, developed using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It currently includes key pages like **Home**, **Products**, **Blog**, and **Sign In**, with plans to expand functionality (e.g., Ordering page, backend integration) in future development.

